title: 51459 The Urban-Rural Impact on Skin Cancer for Skin of Color
details: R Lin, A Maderal, S Elman - Journal of the American Academy of Dermatology, 2024
abstract: Despite health disparities in rural communities being well-documented, few studies evaluate the impact of urban-rural status on skin cancer prevalence in skin of color (SOC). Therefore, a cross-sectional study was conducted on responses from the …
